HEADWORD: Beseen
<hw>Be*seen"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Properly the p. p.
of <ets>besee</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Seen; appearing.</def> <mark>[Obs. or
